abstract: The most curious aspect of the British situation in South Africa is the amount of credible news that leaks out, past a British censorship and over cables of which every one is in British possession. abstract: PRINCETON, N.J., Nov. 12. -- The Princeton football team returned home to-day, happy after the victory over the Carlisle Indians at Manhattan Field Saturday. She was nursing a sick friend, Miss Alice Pierson, who has been ill for months, and has been living with her in her Chester home for more than two months.
